snippet.title: Key Hunters:DX - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Key Hunters DX is a remake of the original Sonic & Knuckles Key Hunters fangame made by Illias Studio. This fangame puts a twist on things by changing the objective of the stages to be akin to the Emerald Radar stages for Knuckles in the Sonic Adventure Series. It boasts some new and returning features and sets out to be a improved and polished experience.

Download the demo and the original Key Hunters here!
https://sites.google.com/view/sonic-project-twisted/homepage/downloads

Disclaimer :
Key Hunters DX is in no way affiliated with Sega or Sonic Team. Its a non profit project created by fans of the original series
